These scripts were used in the paper: https://arxiv.org/submit/2583113/view, also available at https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/8491045.
The arXiv version is as (finally) submitted modulo a small correction in equation (9) that I noticed after publication. 


If you use these scripts in research, please cite: 
T. Cuvelier and R. W. Heath, "MmWave MU-MIMO for Aerial Networks," 2018 15th International Symposium on Wireless Communication Systems (ISWCS), Lisbon, 2018, pp. 1-6. 
Available at: https://arxiv.org/submit/2583113/view
